    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable ride that won't break the bank? This vehicle is a solid choice and ready for its next owner! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its years on the road, it remains a dependable driver that gets the job done. It\u2019s the perfect opportunity to own a well-loved car with plenty of character at a great price!",
